description:
Table `Ptp`:  Point-to-point link data containing timestamps, area, cell identifiers, and Ericsson-specific attributes.

`dateTime`: Timestamp of the point-to-point link data record.
`Area_Name`: Geographical area where the point-to-point link is located.
`CellId`: Unique identifier for the cell at one end of the point-to-point link.
`Id2`:  Secondary identifier, potentially redundant with CellId.
`Id3`:  An identifier with unknown meaning (needs further investigation).
`vsDataType`: Data type indicator specifying point-to-point data.
`vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
`Ptp.ptpId`:  Unique identifier for the point-to-point link itself.
